            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1220979/">爱就好好爱吧</a></h2>

                <div id="review_1220979_short" class="review-short" data-rid="1220979">
                    <div class="short-content">
                            <p class="spoiler-tip">这篇书评可能有关键情节透露</p>

